<DATE>
<P>
April 21, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 3; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
