<DOCNO> LA042194-0161 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 034253 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 21, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
