EAST VALLEY FOCUS: COMMUNITY CENTER'S OPENING POSTPONED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ED BOND 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The grand opening for a new community center in Sun Valley -- which would have 
been held today -- has been pushed back two weeks, said the president of the 
Sun Valley Chamber of Commerce. 
</P>
<P>
 Timing and schedule conflicts delayed the opening of the center, said chamber 
