 GATES & SONS BAR-B-Q 1221 Brooklyn St . ; (816) 483-3880 1411 Swope Parkway; 
(816) 921-0409 2001 W. 103rd Terrace; (913) 383-1752 1026 State Ave.; (913) 
621-1134 810440 E. 40 Highway; (816) 353-5880 215 Rawhide Drive; (913) 764-6210 
Upscale cafeterias serving great ribs, lamb and "top-tier" sauce. The 
atmosphere is fast-food, but the chain's popularity has caused new ones to pop 
