753-1009 The original location for this charming cafe is a Westport coffee, 
specialty grocery and classical music store, but the new location is equally 
attractive, with seating on the sidewalk and back deck. Highlights from the 
menu include a vegetarian club sandwich and strawberry Brie pancakes. Also 
popular for its unusual desserts. Food: 24 Decor: 17 Service: 20 Cost: $15 
