<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFCASE: MARKETING AND MEDIA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Anne Michaud, Times staff writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Fast-Track PR: Nelson Communications Group in Irvine is the fastest-growing 
public relations agency in the Western United States and third-fastest in the 
nation, according to a 1994 survey by O'Dwyer's PR Services Report. 
</P>
<P>
 Robert E. Nelson, chairman and chief executive, credited the company's growth 
to the experience of his staff. They include former TV and newspaper 
journalists, corporate communications executives, local elected officials and 
former political press officers. 
</P>
<P>
 Clients include Anheuser-Busch, the California Teachers Assn., Deloitte & 
Touche, Home Depot, Koll Real Estate Group and San Diego Gas & Electric. 
</P>
