</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Restaurant on Rye to Go: Two retail real estate brokers for Lee & Associates 
in Irvine have begun a one-page restaurant newsletter, printing news about 
available properties, restaurant openings and advice. 
</P>
<P>
 The "Restaurant Real Estate Fax" is distributed to fax machines, and editor 
John Hall said he is hoping the newsletter will prompt restaurateurs to 
communicate back. 
</P>
<P>
 "We wanted to be in the know, and to make a few bucks from being in the know," 
Hall said. His partner is John Moss. They can be reached at (714) 727-1200. 
