<HEADLINE>
<P>
ASIAN AMERICAN MEDIA GUIDE OFFERED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In response to the growing number of Asian American media outlets in the 
United States, the Imada Wong Communications Group in Los Angeles has compiled 
a "1994 Asian Pacific American Media Guide." 
</P>
<P>
 The guide includes more than 500 media sources nationwide, including the 
ethnic and language groups they serve. 
</P>
<P>
 The guide is $395 for businesses, $350 for nonprofit groups. For more 
information, contact Garrett Gin at the Asian News Service, (213) 622-6513. 
</P>
