</P>
<P>
 Connecticut's Forebitter, acclaimed performers of seaworthy songs and stories, 
teams with local storyteller Ed Dobyns to present music and yarns Saturday, 
April 23, at 7:30 p.m. at the Dana Point Youth Group Facility, 34451 Ensenada 
Place. $7 to $11. Call (714) 496-2274. 
</P>
<P>
