<HEADLINE>
<P>
INSIDE LINE: HOMEWORK HELP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Having schoolwork problems at home? Turn to the professionals. 
</P>
<P>
 McDonnell Douglas, an aerospace facility in Huntington Beach, operates a 
Homework Hotline from 6 to 8 p.m. Tuesdays and Thursdays.Employee volunteers, 
mostly engineers and accountants, work the phones to offer help.  
</P>
<P>
 Have the pros ever been stumped? Some high school chemistry and physics 
problems have given volunteers a run for their money, said one hot line helper, 
but brainstorming usually provides a solution. 
</P>
<P>
 The hot line has been operating for about one year. For homework help, call 
(714) 896-5569 or (800) 876-3867. 
</P>
</TEXT>
