</P>
<P>
 Name: Matt Hartman School: California Year: Senior Points: 17.6 
</P>
<P>
 Name: Erik Kennady School: Warren Year: Senior Points: 18.0 
</P>
<P>
 Name: Jason Reynolds School: St. Paul Year: Senior Points: 15.0 
</P>
<P>
